    "In the context of direct sensorimotor grounding and indirect verbal grounding, do both teacher and learner need direct grounding?",
    "If not, why not?",
    "GPT-4: Direct Sensorimotor Grounding (DSG): DSG involves connecting words and concepts to realworld experiences and understandings through direct sensorimotor interactions, especially category learning.",
